Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Republicans head for Texas
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043xf0z
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 19 Aug 1984
How will the new ethnic mix of Dallas react to the influx of Republicans when the convention comes to town? This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less